02:18:51.22 --> 02:18:53.22
And you kick the little fish wire.

1779
02:18:53.22 --> 02:18:53.94
You can't see it.

1780
02:18:53.94 --> 02:18:55.90
And that's what closed the circuit rather than a pressure

1781
02:18:55.90 --> 02:18:56.30
plate.

