1788
02:19:15.34 --> 02:19:17.54
And Decker, my third squad leader,

1789
02:19:17.54 --> 02:19:19.66
turns to me and says, can I go back with them too?

1790
02:19:19.66 --> 02:19:22.82
Because these guys, they're going to get us killed.

1791
02:19:22.82 --> 02:19:24.42
And I just had a son on this deployment.

