02:19:34.50 --> 02:19:38.54
And I'm like, hey, Decker, if stuff goes sideways out here,

1797
02:19:38.54 --> 02:19:41.30
I need at least one other person I know that I can rely on.

1798
02:19:41.30 --> 02:19:43.18
Like, sorry, you got to stay.

1799
02:19:46.18 --> 02:19:48.70
And he's not happy about it, but Roger.

1800
02:19:48.70 --> 02:19:52.14
And you still couldn't convince the new lieutenant, like, hey,

1801
02:19:52.14 --> 02:19:54.62
bro, remember when I said this was a bad idea?

1802
02:19:54.62 --> 02:19:59.30
We just got the absolute luckiest thing we could have ever

1803
02:19:59.30 --> 02:19:59.90
hoped for.

