missed at least one IED that should have had a pretty big

1812
02:20:18.50 --> 02:20:20.34
signature coming off a 105 shell.

1813
02:20:20.34 --> 02:20:23.18
So he's going to re-sweep if we're going to push through

1814
02:20:23.18 --> 02:20:23.70
this field.

